ler |title=Michael Brown protests in Ferguson: When the police dehumanise a community, it shames all of us |date=August 14, 2014 |accessdate=August 20, 2014 |website=Metro |url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/08/14/michael-brown-protests-in-ferguson-when-the-police-dehumanise-a-community-it-shames-all-of-us-4832742/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817182837/http://metro.co.uk/2014/08/14/michael-brown-protests-in-ferguson-when-the-police-dehumanise-a-community-it-shames-all-of-us-4832742/ |archivedate=August 17, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=MLive.Churches>{{cite news |first=Michelle D. |last=Anderson |title=Muskegon-area churches to participate in 'Black Lives Matter' movement on Sunday |date=December 13, 2014 |accessdate=June 30, 2015 |publisher=MLive.com |url=http://www.mlive.com/news/muskegon/index.ssf/2014/12/muskegon-area_churches_to_part.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526113657/http://www.mlive.com/news/muskegon/index.ssf/2014/12/muskegon-area_churches_to_part.html |archivedate=May 26, 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!-- see WP:HIGHBEAM for info about HighBeam, including how to get a free HighBeam account -->\n<!--ref name=MLM.Bar>{{cite web |first=Allyssa D. |last=Dudley |title=National Bar Association Files Suit against Ferguson, Police Department |date=August 19, 2014 |accessdate=December 15, 2014 |publisher=Missouri Lawyers Media |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-37103034.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329081027/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-37103034.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=March 29, 2015 |url-access=subscription |via=HighBeam Research}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=MotherJones.Flowers>{{cite news |first=Mark |last=Follman |title=Michael Brown's Mom Laid Flowers Where He Was Shot\u2014and Police Crushed Them |date=August 27, 2014 |accessdate=August 28, 2014 |website=Mother Jones |url=http://www.motherjones.com/politics/2014/08/ferguson-st-louis-police-tactics-dogs-michael-brown |archive