ate fund-raising pages for Michael Brown's family, cop Darren Wilson after Ferguson shooting |date=August 21, 2014 |accessdate=April 20, 2015 |website=Daily News|location=New York |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/fundraising-pages-michael-brown-family-officer-darren-wilson-article-1.1912298 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150222050859/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/fundraising-pages-michael-brown-family-officer-darren-wilson-article-1.1912298 |archivedate=February 22, 2015 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<!--ref name=NYDailyNews.Stage>{{cite news |first=Kerry |last=Burke |first2=Chelsia Rose |last2=Marcius |first3=Bill |last3=Hutchinson |title=New Yorkers stage demonstrations over Michael Brown shooting in Ferguson, Mo., march on Times Square |date=August 15, 2014 |accessdate=August 21, 2014 |website=Daily News|location=New York |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/new-yorkers-stage-demonstrations-michael-brown-article-1.1904265}}</ref-->\n\n<!--ref name=NYDailyNews.Suspect>{{cite news |first=Meg |last=Wagner |first2=Joe |last2=Kemp |first3=Corky |last3=Semaszko |title=Ferguson cop Darren Wilson didn't know Michael Brown was robbery suspect at time of shooting, chief admits as teen's backers cry character 'assassination' |date=August 15, 2014 |accessdate=November 17, 2014 |website=Daily News|location=New York |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/darren-wilson-identified-killed-18-year-old-michael-brown-article-1.1904539 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828211847/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/darren-wilson-identified-killed-18-year-old-michael-brown-article-1.1904539 |archivedate=August 28, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref-->\n\n<ref name=NYer.Cop>{{cite news |first=Jake |last=Halpern |title=The Cop |date=August 10, 2015 |accessdate=August 11, 2015 |website=The New Yorker |url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2015/08/10/the-cop |quote=Wilson said that he had interviewed for a few police positions but had 