 crowd after shooting: 'Kill the police' |date=August 10, 2014 |accessdate=August 26, 2014 |publisher=Yahoo! News |url=https://news.yahoo.com/missouri-crowd-shooting-kill-police-230624269.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812202107/http://news.yahoo.com/missouri-crowd-shooting-kill-police-230624269.html |archivedate=August 12, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Yahoo.Feds>{{cite news |first=Holbrook |last=Mohr |first2=David A. |last2=Lieb |title=Feds: Evidence Backs Ferguson Officer's Account in Shooting |date=March 4, 2015 |accessdate=March 9, 2015 |website=Yahoo! News |agency=Associated Press |url=https://news.yahoo.com/feds-evidence-backs-ferguson-officers-account-shooting-204518582.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150307043844/http://news.yahoo.com/feds-evidence-backs-ferguson-officers-account-shooting-204518582.html |archivedate=March 7, 2015}}</ref>\n\n<!--ref name=Yahoo.Honor>{{cite news |first=Jason |last=Sickles |title=Photos: Ferguson Officer Darren Wilson earned police honor before fatal shooting |date=August 16, 2014 |accessdate=August 26, 2014 |publisher=Yahoo! News |url=https://news.yahoo.com/photos-ferguson-officer-darren-wilson-received-police-award-earlier-this-year-021255893.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818114720/http://news.yahoo.com/photos-ferguson-officer-darren-wilson-received-police-award-earlier-this-year-021255893.html |archivedate=August 18, 2014 |url-status=live}}</ref-->\n\n<ref name=Yahoo.Report>{{cite news |first=Jason |last=Sickles |title=Key report in Michael Brown shooting doesn't exist, Ferguson police say |date=September 25, 2014 |accessdate=September 27, 2014 |publisher=Yahoo! News |url=https://news.yahoo.com/ferguson-police-internal-record-on-controversial-shooting-of-michael-brown-doesnt-exist-001401818.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140928180543/http://news.yahoo.com/ferguson-police-internal-record-on-controversial-shooting-of-michael-brown-doesnt-exist-