-span.org/video/?322925-1/ferguson-missouri-grand-jury-decision-announcement Video of statement at end of grand jury along with press conference] and [https://www.stltoday.com/news/local/crime-and-courts/statement-of-st-louis-prosecuting-attorney-robert-p-mcculloch/article_2becfef3-9b4b-5e1e-9043-f586f389ef91.html transcript of statement]\n* [https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2015/03/04/us/doj-report-on-shooting-of-michael-brown.html DOJ investigation report into shooting]\n* [http://documents.latimes.com/michael-browns-family-files-civil-lawsuit-against-ferguson/ Michael Brown\u2019s family's civil lawsuit against Ferguson]\n\n{{2014 Ferguson unrest}}\n{{Black Lives Matter}}\n{{Authority  control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Brown, Michael}}\n[[Category:Shooting of Michael Brown| ]]\n[[Category:2014 controversies in the United States]]\n[[Category:2014 in Missouri]]\n[[Category:African-American history of Missouri]]\n[[Category:African-American-related controversies]]\n[[Category:August 2014 events in the United States]]\n[[Category:Civil rights protests in the United States]]\n[[Category:Crimes in Missouri]]\n[[Category:Defensive gun use]]\n[[Category:History of African-American civil rights]]\n[[Category:History of St. Louis County, Missouri]]\n[[Category:Media-related controversies in the United States]]\n[[Category:Race and crime in the United States]]\n[[Category:Self-defense]]\n", "name_user": "2600:387:0:80d::79", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Typo)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shooting_of_Michael_Brown"}
